{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"HTMLInputElement: invalid イベント","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/invalid_event","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement\"><code>HTMLInputElement</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/files\"><code>files</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/labels\"><code>labels</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/multiple\"><code>multiple</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/webkitdirectory\"><code>webkitdirectory</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/webkitEntries\"><code>webkitEntries</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/checkValidity\"><code>checkValidity()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/reportValidity\"><code>reportValidity()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/select\"><code>select()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/setCustomValidity\"><code>setCustomValidity()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/setRangeText\"><code>setRangeText()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/setSelectionRange\"><code>setSelectionRange()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/showPicker\"><code>showPicker()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/stepDown\"><code>stepDown()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/stepUp\"><code>stepUp()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>イベント</summary><ol><li><em><code>invalid</code></em></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/search_event\"><code>search</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/select_event\"><code>select</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/selectionchange_event\"><code>selectionchange</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>継承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong><code>invalid</code></strong> イベントは、送信可能な要素が制約の検証を受け、制約を満たしていない場合に発行されます。</p>\n<table class=\"properties\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">バブリング</th>\n      <td>なし</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">キャンセル</th>\n      <td>可</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">インターフェイス</th>\n      <td><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">イベントハンドラープロパティ</th>\n      <td><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/invalid_event\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>GlobalEventHandlers.oninvalid</code></a></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n<p>このイベントは、送信時にフォームの問題の概要を表示するのに便利です。フォームが送信されると、 <code>invalid</code> イベントがそれぞれの妥当ではない状態にあるフォームコントロールで発生します。送信可能な要素が妥当であるかどうかは、その所有者である <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/form\"><code>&lt;form&gt;</code></a> を送信する前、または <a href=\"/ja/docs/Learn/Forms#constraint_validation_api\"><code>checkValidity()</code></a> メソッドがその要素またはその所有者である <code>&lt;form&gt;</code> に呼び出された後にチェックされます。</p>\n<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Element/blur_event\" title=\"blur\"><code>blur</code></a> ではチェックが行われません。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>フォームが無効な値で送信された場合、送信可能な要素がチェックされ、エラーが見つかった場合、無効な要素で <code>invalid</code> イベントが発生します。この例では、入力に無効な値があったために <code>invalid</code> イベントが発生した場合、無効な値がログに記録されます。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html","title":"HTML","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>form</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">action</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>#<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>label</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>1 から 10 までの整数を入力してください: <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">min</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">max</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>10<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">required</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>label</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>submit<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">value</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>送信<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>form</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>log<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"javascript","title":"JavaScript","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> input <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'input'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> log <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'log'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\ninput<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'invalid'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> logValue<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">logValue</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  log<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>textContent <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"結果","title":"結果","isH3":true,"content":"<iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"例\" id=\"frame_examples\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/invalid_event/_sample_.examples.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"仕様書","id":"仕様書","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/indices.html#event-invalid","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.HTMLInputElement.invalid_event"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"ブラウザーの互換性","isH3":false,"query":"api.HTMLInputElement.invalid_event","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/invalid_event/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"関連情報","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>HTML の <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/form\"><code>&lt;form&gt;</code></a> element</li>\n  <li>関連イベント: <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLFormElement/submit_event\" title=\"submit\"><code>submit</code></a></li>\n  <li>CSS の <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/:invalid\"><code>:invalid</code></a> 擬似クラス</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"例","id":"例"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"仕様書"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"ブラウザーの互換性"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"関連情報"}],"summary":"invalid イベントは、送信可能な要素が制約の検証を受け、制約を満たしていない場合に発行されます。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"HTMLInputElement: invalid event","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Evento invalid","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"invalid","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"HTMLInputElement: invalid event","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/htmlinputelement/invalid_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/htmlinputelement